    "summary": "In this conversation, a user expresses profound shame and hopelessness following total financial and personal ruin, hinting at suicidal ideation. The assistant consistently responds with empathy, validates the user's feelings of pain while refuting their self-perception as a failure, and repeatedly directs them to professional crisis resources and helplines.",
